headline: ADM, Alltech to Bring Together Unparalleled Expertise and Experience in New North American Animal Feed Joint Venture
summary: CHICAGO & LEXINGTON, Ky., September 23, 2025--ADM (NYSE: ADM), a global leader in innovative solutions from nature, and Alltech, a global leader in agriculture, today announced the signing of a definitive agreement to launch a North American animal feed joint venture, bringing together decades of experience and unparalleled capabilities to create new advantages for customers.
